{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"69ed05900f","title":"接见军队领导干部时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a8da1e616c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":13,"articleId":"69ed05900f"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"d48f0ea3e8","name":"造反运动和派别斗争","type":"主题"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"30ad9a64e1","type":"title","text":"接见军队领导干部时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f"},{"id":"4edad40b7f","type":"paragraph","text":"不要怕闹，闹得越大、越长，越好。七闹八闹，总会闹出名堂来的，可以闹清楚。不管怎么闹，不要怕，越怕鬼越来。但也不要开枪，什么时候开枪也是不好的。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f"},{"id":"ebda064af7","type":"paragraph","text":"全国大闹不可能。那里有脓包，有细菌，总要爆发的。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f"},{"id":"21654ba6cc","type":"paragraph","text":"南京街上闹得很厉害，我越看越高兴。闹得第三派那么多人，反对内战，反对武斗，这很好嘛！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f"},{"id":"34a52bae97","type":"paragraph","text":"（张春桥：有人讲第三派是走第三条道路的。）","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f"},{"id":"8c17b600d5","type":"paragraph","text":"哪有什么第三条道路呀！人家要大联合，大批判，你要诱导嘛！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f"}],"page":{"id":"42bd3c3bd5","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"69ed05900f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}